=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )=E2=80=9D Shapiro is back today with some chatter fr=
om the C.P.G. world, an update from the affiliate-marketing trenches, and a=
 dispatch from your local, perfectly manicured outdoor shopping center, whe=
re there is almost undoubtedly a Madewell.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

What happened to Madewell,
anyway? It was once the kinda-cool alternative to J.Crew. But instead of co=
ntinuing to chase the youth, it aged up with Millennial women, who are now =
moms hanging out at=E2=80=A6 outdoor shopping centers. The problem for Made=
well is that those shoppers have more choices now.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

As you know, I=E2=80=99m in Europe this week. I=E2=80=99ll be back tomorrow=
 with an update on the layoffs at Saks Global and the town hall that took
place today. But before heading to Milan on Wednesday night, I had some cat=
